Statements:

Store some value : variables

1. dataType variableName= value;

2. dataType variableName;  int x;
                            x =10;

Statements: make some decision

if-else statement [single decision]
   if(condition)
   {
       code here will execute only if condition is true
   }
   else
   {
       code here will execute only if condition is false
   }


if-else if statement [multiple decision]

   if(condition1)
   {
       code here will execute only if condition1 is true
   }
   else if(condition2)
   {
       code here will execute only if condition2 is true
   }
   else if(condition3)
   {
      code here will execute only if condition3 is true
   }
   ..
   ..
   ..
   ..
   else if(conditionN)
   {
      code here will execute only if conditionN is true
   }
   else
   {
       code here will execute only if condition is false
   }


switch statement
 it only supports these data types
   byte/short/int/char/String